🐟 Fish Feeder Arduino - Include Directory
=========================================

This directory contains all header files for the modular Fish Feeder system.

📁 Structure:
├── sensor_data.h        - Global data structures and pin definitions
├── sensor_service.h     - Master sensor management service
├── dht_sensor.h         - DHT22 temperature/humidity sensors
├── water_temp_sensor.h  - DS18B20 water temperature sensor
├── weight_sensor.h      - HX711 load cell with calibration
├── soil_sensor.h        - Analog soil moisture sensor
├── voltage_sensor.h     - Battery voltage monitoring
├── acs712_sensor.h      - ACS712 solar current sensor
└── blower.h            - Blower motor control

🎯 Design Philosophy:
- Clean separation of concerns
- Each sensor has its own class with standard interface
- Global instances for easy access
- Error checking and validation
- Emoji-based status output

🔧 Usage:
Include the main service headers in your main.cpp:
#include "sensor_data.h"
#include "sensor_service.h"

Then initialize with:
sensorService.begin();

📚 Dependencies:
- DHT sensor library
- OneWire library  
- DallasTemperature library
- HX711 library 